ingredients.ingredient: ½ (8 ounce) package cream cheese, at room temperature
¼ (16 ounce) package wonton wrappers, at room temperature

cookingTips: Keep wonton wrappers covered with a damp towel to prevent drying out
Use a small amount of water on wrapper edges to seal properly
Fry at 350°F until golden brown, about 2-3 minutes per side
